{"tid":1940371,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]林鄭到訪將軍澳名校紅華湘","createTime":"2020-03-23T17:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T18:55:59.000Z","uid":259462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10c4961fb95d7ffd9e124bb2b678dffc810e01c2","tid":1940371,"uid":259462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[轉貼] 今日我到訪將軍澳的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仁濟醫院<del>王</del>紅華湘中學</span></strong>，了解學校在停課期間如何運用多種電子學習軟件，以保持學生的學習動力和興趣，亦與幾位同學視像交談。現時很多學校採用不同方法支援學生學習，政府亦為基層家庭學生上網學習提供支援，包括透過關愛基金資助他們購買流動電腦裝置，而「防疫抗疫基金」亦已增加每位學生的津貼，可幫補家長購買電子學習裝置的支出。<br />\n</span><br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B-FEzM8gj9V/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-FEzM8gj9V%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1pmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=2038836c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-FEzM8gj9V%2F&h=75fcf56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B-FEzM8gj9V/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1f9jAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1f9jAP.png&h=18fa1917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k10AZAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk10AZAT.png&h=8475307a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更多閱讀：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">強烈譴責將軍澳名校校長語言暴力行為促連登仔嚴厲執法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1210618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1210618/page/1</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"0fa87b592f0f0383377db56885aa7e930e952268","tid":1940371,"uid":259462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"介紹返<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅華湘校長</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.imgur.com/nDhovLR.jpg\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">姓名：邱Ｘ雄<br />\n學校：仁Ｘ醫院Ｘ華湘中學<br />\n公職：校長，新界校Ｘ會主席<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邱Ｘ雄帶領的新界校Ｘ會對近日示威活動發表強烈譴責並表明不認同</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【橙訊】經過示威者凌晨一輪衝擊後，立法會示威區鐵馬亂疊如山，遍地垃圾。新界校長會發表聲明，指《基本法》保障市民遊行、示威的權利，惟有人故意破壞秩序，煽動群眾，企圖造成混亂，該會堅決反對此等惡劣行為，並強烈譴責任何形式的暴力，並促請警方嚴厲執法。<br />\n<br />\n該會表示，相信香港市民都是守法，並尊重市民上街遊行，以和平的方式表達意見。遊行過程和平有序，向世界展示香港確有言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n該會又批評，有一小撮滋事份子，沒聽從警方勸籲，更出現暴力行為，導致有警員和記者受傷，令事件蒙污，對此表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n相關網址：<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/06/10/010118708.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F010118708.shtml&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1pmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=85cda226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/06/10/010118708.shtml</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.imgur.com/FkQhFms.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.imgur.com/kiKCtvm.png\" />"},{"pid":"d59613d51b4ec23689d7bea0d9ce1bffbbaeefd4","tid":1940371,"uid":129733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"其實香港大部份校長都係藍/紅，係差在佢哋會唔會show出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b95356695a04899b26e2f9fb7212fb4108adaf","tid":1940371,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d59613d51b4ec23689d7bea0d9ce1bffbbaeefd4","tid":1940371,"uid":129733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"其實香港大部份校長都係藍/紅，係差在佢哋會唔會show出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"王華湘應該係區內最紅"},{"pid":"34c57b0429f1dd4fee6ed88940c72132987900e8","tid":1940371,"uid":79207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d59613d51b4ec23689d7bea0d9ce1bffbbaeefd4","tid":1940371,"uid":129733,"like":2,"